description: Prestigious hidden Gem in Prime Gated Location of Avalon at Seven Meadows. This extravagant Custom home offers  Double Doors to a Grand Living area with 25Ft Ceiling which features seamless glass to the panoramic views of the Infinity pool/spa, lakes and fountain. The Gourmet Kitchen has top tier appliances, waterfall granite countertops, butler's pantry. Full Wet bar/wine grotto, A grand dining room with domed ceiling. The luxurious Owners suite boasts a fireplace/sitting area/walk-in double entry shower and access to the outside patio. Bedrooms have great views and ensuite with walk in closets. The grand 6th bedroom can be home office or guest suite, large game room with wet bar and its own half bath, study station and gym, A very Cinema type gorgeous Theatre room. Also from the upstairs Balcony you can Enjoy the full lake views relaxing water fountain,  it's just amazing to relax!  Zoned for highly rated Katy ISD Schools!! Home wont last!
